title: SIP 29 meme contest v2!
body:
A handful of members of the community have proposed a meme contest! Lets see what the community thinks!

Should we have a meme contest? Or no?

I want to propose a community vote on having a meme contest.

This will help community engagement and help incentivize new members to participate in the convo!

120 SGT in total will be used from the treasury. Winners will receive: 

1st: 60 SGT
2nd: 40 SGT
3rd: 20 SGT 
-----------------------------------
To enter the draw you must:
- Submit your meme. You may submit as many memes as you want to.
- Follow @SharedStakeOrg and @ChimeraDefi on Twitter.
- Like and retweet the SharedStake meme competition twitter post.


This helps Sharedstake get more exposure and benefit from degen marketing tactics
author: 0xa1feaF41d843d53d0F6bEd86a8cF592cE21C409e
